---
description: Core project goal and non-negotiable scope
alwaysApply: true
---

This project is "My Address, My City".

The product is a resident-friendly civic web app for Montgomery, Alabama.

Its purpose is to turn one address or one clicked map location into a useful civic snapshot.

The app must remain:
- simple
- explainable
- resident-facing
- demoable in 60-90 seconds

Avoid turning this into:
- a generic GIS viewer
- a complex dashboard
- a chatbot-first product
- a broad smart-city platform
